{{flavour|A magical device which throws little bits of frost.}}

A '''wand of frost''' has the same effect as the spell [[Throw Frost]], but with greater range and accuracy. Its damage output is based on your [[Evocations]] skill, but never becomes very impressive. It is inferior to the [[wand of cold]]. It can have at most 48 charges.

==History==
*Wands of frost were removed in [[0.18]].
*Prior to [[0.16]], this wand could hold up to 24 charges.
